# Privacy Policy

**Effective Date:** 2024-01-01

**1. Introduction**
This application ("Marketing Data Fetcher") is a private tool created by [你的名字/GitHub ID] for internal use only. It is designed to retrieve advertising performance data from the Meta Marketing API.

**2. Data Collection**
This application accesses data from your Meta Ad Accounts (e.g., spend, impressions, clicks). We do not collect personal user information (PII) of your customers.

**3. Data Usage**
The data retrieved is used solely for the purpose of internal data analysis and reporting.

**4. Data Sharing**
We do not sell, trade, or otherwise transfer your data to outside parties. All data remains within your controlled environment (e.g., your local database or BigQuery).

**5. Contact**
If you have any questions, please contact: lutuhack0788@gmail.com
